{"tid":1727133,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"(拋豬引肉）如何解決/處理催淚煙的影響","createTime":"2019-11-16T10:40:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T10:42:13.000Z","uid":325542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8b071de5755641b5a157e09e01768e2fc388e49f","tid":1727133,"uid":325542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:40:07.000Z","msg":"中共製催淚彈會釋出二噁英(dioxin)，而二噁英對人體傷害係唔可以逆轉，特別係生育能力。中共依家係隻香港人嘅手去慢性毒害港人同佢哋嘅下一代，形同絕育。港大化學系博士、前暴大講師 K Kwong 話件事衰過福島核事故，究竟點樣先可以救香港？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我諗過用冷凍精子、卵子技術，希望能夠令港人留下種子，免墮入中共圈套。但係未知香港夠唔夠技術處理咁多冷凍精、卵子；而且採集卵子嗰陣，醫生會用藥物去刺激卵巢排出更多卵子（不用藥通常只會排出一個），可能會誘發卵巢癌同其他致命風險，更有機會令BB出現好幾種嚴重異常，好似發展遲緩、骨骼發育遲緩、增加罹患兒童癌症嘅風險;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />另外呢啲技術收費亦都唔平，一般來講都係超過成萬。<br />\n所以希望各位諗一諗點樣可以救港，免入中共圈套...... 唔一定係用醫學方法作出發點，僅此希望可以集思廣益，搵到一個可行方法幫手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://m.commonhealth.com.tw/article/article.action?nid=64990\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.commonhealth.com.tw%2Farticle%2Farticle.action%3Fnid%3D64990&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQJE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=298c4d24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.commonhealth.com.tw/article/article.action?nid=64990</a>"},{"pid":"0a98962326e380a562e98d575562b19fd8028a87","tid":1727133,"uid":325542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:40:32.000Z","msg":"自推 1/10"},{"pid":"2a8bf546aa4c5075429ad69aedfcc05ceb61563d","tid":1727133,"uid":325542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:40:44.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"39561bb9433cb3facdc6444eddf614f9e967423f","tid":1727133,"uid":325542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:40:55.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"c7b2225a4d1950befbd80224a5467c5ed0bdee47","tid":1727133,"uid":325542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:41:06.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"6df1340ff7148b9239aead72d62adb230926ed20","tid":1727133,"uid":325542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:41:16.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"dd9e8cd31658f11a5c50faf1699f01524010896d","tid":1727133,"uid":325542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:41:26.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"95253dcce2fe09f3d0710eaef0d305cc4dbb6d90","tid":1727133,"uid":325542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:41:42.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"216497055ac535dd7c495ea5282d04900d91195f","tid":1727133,"uid":325542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:41:52.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"50950d9e95286a6c85d8ea08edd1b921a7915f60","tid":1727133,"uid":325542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:42:02.000Z","msg":"9/10"},{"pid":"6acfc57b46071793a55ee94501eb328922d62136","tid":1727133,"uid":325542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:42:13.000Z","msg":"10/10"}]}